column5: how's the perch bite been with all the rain and wind thinking of going up for a day and getting a taged fish
A lot of little dinks, maybe not warm enough yet.  I did all the way out to about 25 feet, absolutely nothing, caught a few keepers in tthe marina.
corvette we'll be there Fri&Sat. Nothing but dinks last week in the marina. Hope there's a few big ones out deeper this week.
Everyone's been trying to find the jumbo's, myself included... nowhere to be found as of yet, I've also hit the deeper and nothing at all
